text: Sulzbach is a town and a city in the district of Saarbrücken, in Saarland, Germany. It has a population of 16,215 (as of Dec 2015). It is located northeast of Saarbrücken. ==References== Category:Cities in Saarland Category:Towns in Saarland Category:Saarbrücken (district)
title: Sulzbach, Saarland
